text: Langbach (also: Röhlesbach or Roderbach) is a small river of North Rhine- Westphalia and Rhineland-Palatinate, Germany. It is a right tributary of the Kyll near Frauenkron. ==See also== *List of rivers of Rhineland-Palatinate == References == Category:Rivers of the Eifel Category:Rivers of Rhineland- Palatinate Category:Rivers of Germany
title: Langbach (Kyll)
